title: Jonny Cat Litter Box Liners: Heavy Duty - Tear & Leak Resistant - Drawstring Close - Jumbo, 15 Count
description: Jonny Cat Heavy Duty Tear-Resistant Litter Box Liners are 2 MIL thick so cats' claws and paws can't rip through them. With no waste or spillage stuck to the litter box, Jonny Cat Liners make cleanup easy. Simply pull the convenient drawstring, close, and dispose. No mess, no stress!
